close_reason: "Work fully landed on main. The 2026-05-31 late-main audit's actionable output (query-flag-typo explicit-retry guard + mixed-case command classification) reached main via PR #91 (41d366e0) and was confirmed/carried by PR #94 (merge da6a38ef, 2026-06-01) — during the PR #94 merge the canonical main versions of src/cli/main.ts, help-runtime.spec.ts, and this task's tracker were taken. Specialist sub-agent findings were recorded as comments; remaining actionable items are tracked (pm-kcba release-publish gap). All CI checks green on PR #94; merged back to main clean. Acceptance met."
